				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\gamma $$\end{document} rays for the outgoing TOF is achieved by exploiting the PSD capabilities of EJ-309, as exemplified in Fig. 5; γ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
