				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\gamma $$\end{document}-ray selection for the incoming TOF is achieved by selecting low-charge events in the target cell in a given time window, as exemplified in Fig. 6. Efforts to apply PSD-based neutron/γ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
